    "title": "Senior Frontend Developer at Housing.com",
    "description": "Join the Housing.com family as a Frontend Developer in Nashik. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Housing.com:\nHousing.com is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Housing.com!",
